= Wenqi Fan - Openings (Year-round Recruitment)

Prof. *Wenqi Fan* is currently an Assistant Professor of the Department of Computing (Faculty of Engineering) & Department of Management and Marketing (Business School), The Hong Kong Polytechnic University (PolyU). 

Our research group are actively recruiting self-motivated *Postdoc, Ph.D. students, [https://www.polyu.edu.hk/gs/prospective-students/dual-phd-degree-programmes/ Dual PhD Degree students], MPhil/Msc, and Research Assistants*, etc. 
Visiting scholars, interns, and self-funded students are also welcome. 
Send me an email if you are interested. 


 
>>> Research areas: machine learning (ML), data mining (DM), artificial intelligence (AI), deep learning (DNNs), graph neural networks (GNNs), computer vision (CV), natural language processing (NLP), Bioinformatics, etc. 




